          {
            "title": "Intro",
            "id": 74193,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Sites e aplicativos como o abaixo precisam regularmente realizar a mesma tarefa repetidamente.</p><webview version=\"2\" visible-if=\"always\" content=\"&lt;!doctype html&gt;&#xA;&lt;html&gt;&#xA; &lt;head&gt;&#xA;  &lt;style&gt;&#xA;   body {&#xA;    text-align: center;&#xA;    height: 275px;&#xA;    font-size: 16px;&#xA;    margin: 0 auto;&#xA;    background-color: #F0F8FF;&#xA;   }&#xA;   &#xA;   button {&#xA;    background-color: darkBlue;&#xA;    border: none;&#xA;    border-radius: 8px;&#xA;    color: white;&#xA;    text-align: center;&#xA;    text-decoration: none;&#xA;    display: inline-block;&#xA;    font-size: 14px;&#xA;    padding: 6px 12px;&#xA;    margin: 0 12px 0 0;&#xA;   }&#xA;   &#xA;   h2 {&#xA;    text-align: center;&#xA;   }&#xA;   &#xA;   #playerList {&#xA;    text-align: left;&#xA;   }&#xA;  &lt;/style&gt;&#xA; &lt;/head&gt;&#xA; &lt;body&gt;&#xA;  &lt;img height=180 src=&quot;https://mimo.app/i/volume-icon.png&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;  &lt;button onclick=&quot;increase()&quot;&gt;Increase volume&lt;/button&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p id=&quot;container&quot;&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;   &lt;script&gt;&#xA;    let volume = 0;&#xA;    &#xA;    function increase() {&#xA;     document.getElementById(&quot;container&quot;).innerHTML =&#xA;      &quot;Volume increased!&quot;;&#xA;     let s = document.getElementById('container').style;&#xA;     s.display = &quot;block&quot;;&#xA;     s.opacity = 1;&#xA;     (function fade() {&#xA;      if ((s.opacity -= .1) &lt; 0) s.display = &quot;none&quot;;&#xA;      else setTimeout(fade, 150);&#xA;     })();&#xA;    }&#xA;   &lt;/script&gt;&#xA; &lt;/body&gt;&#xA;&lt;/html&gt;\" /></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Intro 2",
            "id": 74468,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Em vez de criar muitos códigos diferentes, os sites usam <strong>funções</strong> para agrupar códigos relacionados e realizar a tarefa em um só lugar.</p><webview version=\"2\" visible-if=\"always\" content=\"&lt;!doctype html&gt;&#xA;&lt;html&gt;&#xA; &lt;head&gt;&#xA;  &lt;style&gt;&#xA;   body {&#xA;    text-align: center;&#xA;    height: 275px;&#xA;    font-size: 16px;&#xA;    margin: 0 auto;&#xA;    background-color: #F0F8FF;&#xA;   }&#xA;   &#xA;   button {&#xA;    background-color: darkBlue;&#xA;    border: none;&#xA;    border-radius: 8px;&#xA;    color: white;&#xA;    text-align: center;&#xA;    text-decoration: none;&#xA;    display: inline-block;&#xA;    font-size: 14px;&#xA;    padding: 6px 12px;&#xA;    margin: 0 12px 0 0;&#xA;   }&#xA;   &#xA;   h2 {&#xA;    text-align: center;&#xA;   }&#xA;   &#xA;   #playerList {&#xA;    text-align: left;&#xA;   }&#xA;  &lt;/style&gt;&#xA; &lt;/head&gt;&#xA; &lt;body&gt;&#xA;  &lt;img height=180 src=&quot;https://mimo.app/i/volume-icon.png&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;  &lt;button onclick=&quot;decrease()&quot;&gt;Decrease volume&lt;/button&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p id=&quot;container&quot;&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;   &lt;script&gt;&#xA;    let volume = 0;&#xA;    &#xA;    function decrease() {&#xA;     document.getElementById(&quot;container&quot;).innerHTML =&#xA;      &quot;Volume decreased!&quot;;&#xA;     let s = document.getElementById('container').style;&#xA;     s.display = &quot;block&quot;;&#xA;     s.opacity = 1;&#xA;     (function fade() {&#xA;      if ((s.opacity -= .1) &lt; 0) s.display = &quot;none&quot;;&#xA;      else setTimeout(fade, 150);&#xA;     })();&#xA;    }&#xA;   &lt;/script&gt;&#xA; &lt;/body&gt;&#xA;&lt;/html&gt;\" /></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Function",
            "id": 74194,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para começar a agrupar código relacionado, começamos codificando a palavra-chave <code>function</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\" codelang=\"javascript\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"8\" /></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>function</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Function name",
            "id": 74181,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Em seguida vem o nome da função em camel case, como <code>greetUser</code>, seguido por parênteses, <code>(</code> e <code>)</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\" codelang=\"javascript\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"greetUser\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"9\" endIndex=\"18\" /><option startIndex=\"18\" endIndex=\"19\" /><option startIndex=\"19\" endIndex=\"20\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>greetUser</code> seguido de <code>(</code> e finalmente <code>)</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Braces",
            "id": 74192,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Chaves <code>{</code> e <code>}</code>, delimitam o bloco de código que pertence à função.</p><code version=\"2\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\" codelang=\"javascript\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"greetUser\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"21\" endIndex=\"22\" /><option startIndex=\"25\" endIndex=\"26\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>{</code> seguido de <code>}</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Between braces",
            "id": 74187,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>O código que queremos agrupar vai entre as chaves. Esta função agrupa duas instruções <code>console.log()</code> relacionadas.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"greetUser\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Good morning Anna&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Welcome back&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"59\" endIndex=\"66\" /><option startIndex=\"66\" endIndex=\"67\" /><option startIndex=\"67\" endIndex=\"70\" /><option startIndex=\"71\" endIndex=\"85\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>console</code> seguido de <code>.</code> e depois <code>log</code>, <code>\"Welcome back\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Calling the function",
            "id": 74183,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para executar o código, precisamos <strong>chamar</strong> a função. Fazemos isso codificando seu nome seguido por parênteses, como <code>greetUser();</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\" codelang=\"javascript\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"greetUser\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Good morning Anna&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Welcome back&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"greetUser();\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"91\" endIndex=\"103\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Good morning Anna\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Welcome back\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>greetUser();</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
