            "title": "Example: Function",
            "id": 74217,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Codifique a palavra-chave <code>function</code> para completar a função.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"weatherUpdate\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Weather update&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Sunny skies ahead&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"weatherUpdate();\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"8\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Weather update\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Sunny skies ahead\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>function</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
